value.0: Hello there! 'ere to buy some fish? Best quality on the Isles, an' don't ye let them snooty buggers at Corwell market tell ye otherwise!

*frowns* o', I see... they pawned ye off on me, did they? *sighs* Aye, if ye can bring me a decent fish I'll pay ye a fair price fer it. 'am no like them, see? Everyone deserves a' fair chance in ma books *nods firmly*

O'course, if'n ye don't want tae sell 'em ye can <StartCheck>gut</Start> the buggers yersel'. Some-time ye may even find somethin <StartCheck>valuable</Start> inside o' them!

Ah see, ye didn't decide tae gut 'em an see if ye could find any gems or 'out, eh?

*sighs* oh aye, well let's see wha' rotters ye've brought me, come on then *looks over your offerings*

In't 'e colourful, eh? Colourful an... tiny. *hands you a coin*

Any more?

A wee tiddler, eh? Still, someone might want et. 'ere's yer coin.

Any more?

Mean-lookin' fella wan't he? Have a bit o' coin fer that'un!

Any more?

No' bad, no' bad.. 'ere, tha's a fair price for 'er

Any more?

Tha's a pretty big one! 'ere, take this gold eh

Any more?

Tha's a whopper! 'ere, take this gold eh

Any more?
You stink, lady! I'm outta here! *leave*
Oh, how I wish for a big fat fish! I'm as hungry as ever could be! A dish of fish is my only wish! How far are we from the sea? *look at her wares*
I heard you might be looking for fresh fish for your stock?
Great! I'll get fishin' and be right back!
I have some fish here with me... will you buy them?
I'll come back later with more fish
Sell Striped bass
Sell Small mouth bass
Sell Pike
Sell Medium sized trout
Sell Large trout
Sell Large mouth bass
